# Backend Pytest Clarity

Apply this when creating or editing backend test files (`backend/tests/**/*.py`).

- Add a short docstring to every test function describing behavior under test.
- Use explanatory assert messages that explain expected behavior.
- Prefer one behavior per test; keep grouped checks tightly related.
- Use explicit `pytest.raises(..., match="...")` for expected exceptions.
